happy new year! 

Is there a possiblity to to clone/duplicate a workspace?

For a presentation I want to use a LibreOffice-presentation (Impress) in presentation-mode (moderators view on workspace I on my screen and presentation in workspace II on beamer).

Beside this I want to show something "step by step" (workspace III on my screen AND beamer) in a certain program. For this I could just clone my displays but then the presentation-mode of Impress doesn't work anymore. 

So is there a way to tell i3 to clone the content of display III to display IV so that everything I do on display III is visible on display IV as well?

Thank you!
